        <mxCell id="mAx34IeTYbzBOSO-Cvki-41" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;fontFamily=Lucida Console;fontSize=11;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Instance Type:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;CX33 x86_64 (4VCpu 8GB RAM)&lt;br&gt;Linux Fedora 42&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Technology&lt;/b&gt;:&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- Dockerized React &amp;amp; Material UI Typescript Frontend served to user /w Nginx Reverse Proxy running on port 443&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- Dockerized Express Typescript Server running on port 8443&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- Dockerized PostGres 17 Database used as endpoint for backend on port 5432&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Constraints:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- Local Image Storage without S3 persistence&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- No&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;connectivity&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;to AWS via API Gateway&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- No connectivity to Cloud Production Database&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- Frontend is clientside, despite backend running locally, dns re-&lt;br&gt;solution &amp;amp; loadbalancer routing via https layer 4 tcp ingress on port 443 via SNI routing is needed for mututal communication&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
