        <mxCell id="mAx34IeTYbzBOSO-Cvki-52" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;fontFamily=Lucida Console;fontSize=11;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Instance Type:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;CX23 x86_64 (2VCpu 4GB RAM)&lt;br&gt;Linux Fedora 42&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Technology&lt;/b&gt;:&lt;br&gt;HAProxy LoadBalancer running as rootless docker container&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Capabilities&lt;/b&gt;:&lt;br&gt;- High-performant layer-4 tcp loadbalancer&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- singular HTTPS Ingress point into entire network&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- SNI based routing to private instances&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;- binary TCP packets are sent from client to private instances fully encrypted, enabling&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;TLS Pass-through for mTLS&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="184" width="229.5" x="1212.5" y="2049.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
